  "title": "高级拉面师傅",
  "description": "<p>负责拉面餐馆的后厨运营</p><p>懂得如何熬煮兰州牛肉面的原汤</p><p>懂得如何兑汤</p><p>懂得如何熬制兰州牛肉面的油泼辣子</p><p>能熟练制作8种面型</p><p>会炒面，煎鸡肉</p><p>能熟练切牛肉，切蒜苗，白萝卜</p><p>能按公司要求准备小菜</p><p>能做好厨房的清洁工作<br /></p><p>In charge of the kitchen operation of a Lanzhou Beef Noodle restaurant</p><p>Knowing how to prepare the beef soup</p><p>Knowing how to prepare the chili sauce for Lanzhou Beef Noodle</p><p>Knowing how to pull 8 different types of noodle</p><p>Can fried noodle and grill chicken</p><p>Can cut beef, Chinese Leek and radish efficiently</p><p>Can prepare side dishes according to company's requirement</p><p>Can do cleaning working according to company's requirement</p>",
